{"tid":2003890,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"昂熱球員因對著鄰居家打飛機被捕，球員認為女鄰居看不到他","createTime":"2020-05-06T06:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T06:28:07.000Z","uid":134997,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"73143c0b59e13f683a629b6ddd2070aee2a12de3","tid":2003890,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:02:51.000Z","msg":"據《巴黎人報》消息，阿爾及利亞國腳、法甲昂熱球員埃爾梅拉利被警方所拘留，其罪名是性暴露癖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據瞭解，在5月5日凌晨，鄰居們發現埃爾梅拉利在自家院子里進行著不可描述的動作，並且目光對準著位於一樓的鄰居家中。<br />\n<br />\n鄰居們隨後報了警，警方逮捕了埃爾梅拉利。據警方消息，這已經是埃爾梅拉利第二次因為類似的行為而被舉報。他的辯護律師表示，埃爾梅拉利這樣做是因為他覺得女鄰居並不會看到他。<br />\n<br />\n據瞭解，埃爾梅拉利已經出庭承認了自己的罪行，目前已經可以返回家中。他將面臨罰款的懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n@夢不拾遺"},{"pid":"e549c3cb6e0ad946f47e695fd998dd93c4802fb2","tid":2003890,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:03:29.000Z","msg":"最尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660c5e689905778f2b85d31df00848e6b58414a2","tid":2003890,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:03:50.000Z","msg":"雞姦犯幾時俾人拉"},{"pid":"dfc86487e7f3087a00d8ff3cbd0d21106b351686","tid":2003890,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"660c5e689905778f2b85d31df00848e6b58414a2","tid":2003890,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:03:50.000Z","msg":"雞姦犯幾時俾人拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:04:51.000Z","msg":"C朗踢波咁勁我一早原諒咗"},{"pid":"660c1cc9dfe915f7584be69359a21cc505223250","tid":2003890,"uid":209225,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:08:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">樓主五毛<br />\n請勿回覆</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ae0ea46587fc73d640bc966e0dfa0c0868517379","tid":2003890,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e549c3cb6e0ad946f47e695fd998dd93c4802fb2","tid":2003890,"uid":60